{
  "stem": "1338.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as Leib is concerned, my dream would have been to find him and bring him to Yad Vashem and make him one of the righteous.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what I was dreaming.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Anyway, selections.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Every Sunday in the regular labor camp that I was in, they would select the Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And usually, they would bring people-- I'm not proud what I'm going to say now.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, we like always to see ourselves-- we-- we do rewrite history.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I think it would be unfair to this project if I was going to sanitize it, even for sake of anybody, including probably myself.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So what I'm going to say probably is not always what I would like.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I know it's probably published.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I know it's publicized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It's a public event.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I prefer not-- but I think that in order to-- to pay tribute to those who did not survive, I think it behooves me to be not only candid, but truthful.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Selections were terrible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Every Sunday, you knew you were going to go.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "One of those selections, I had to beg for life, and got away because I had a good accent, which impressed the block command.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Another one was, for example, they would bring all-- there were a lot of Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This was the Hungarian deportation period.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That's where they brought 400,000 or more-- I don't know the numbers-- of Hungarian Jews during the summer of 1944 to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And most of them were liquidated.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
